{"kanda":6,"sarga":57,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"अकम्पनवधंश्रुत्वाक्रुद्धोवैराक्षसेश्वरः ।किञ्चिददीनमुखश्चापिसचिवांस्तानुदैक्षत","trans":"The king of Rakshasas hearing about the death of Akampana, was pale and a little angry and looked at his ministers.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसेश्वरः","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"अकम्पनवधम्","m":"Akampana's death"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"having heard"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"angry"},{"d":"किञ्चित्","m":"little"},{"d":"दीनमुखःचअपि","m":"with pale face"},{"d":"तान्","m":"his"},{"d":"सचिवान्","m":"ministers"},{"d":"उदैक्षत","m":"looked at."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"सतुध्यात्वामुहूर्तंतुमन्त्रिभिस्संविचार्यच ।ततस्तुरावणःपूर्वदिवसेराक्षसाधिपः पुरींपरिययौलङ्कांसर्वगुल्मानवेक्षितुम् ।","trans":"Ravana, the king of Rakshasas, reflected for a while and deliberated with his ministers and proceeded in the forenoon to inspect all posts in Lanka.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसाधिपः","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"सःरावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"मुहूर्तम्","m":"for a while"},{"d":"ध्यात्वा","m":"reflected"},{"d":"मन्त्रिभिः","m":"ministers too"},{"d":"संविचार्यच","m":"deliberated"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"पूर्वदिवसे","m":"forenoon"},{"d":"सर्वगुल्मान्","m":"all posts"},{"d":"अवेक्षितुम्","m":"inspect"},{"d":"लङ्कांपुरीम्","m":"Lanka city"},{"d":"ययौ","m":"proceeded."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"तांराक्षसगणैर्गुप्तांगुल्मैर्बहुभिरावृताम् ददर्शनगरींलङ्कांपताकाध्वजमालिनीम् ।","trans":"Ravana saw Lanka guarded by the Rakshasa army, surrounded by many posts, with flags, posts, and pennants.","words":[{"d":"लङ्कां","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"राक्षसगणैः","m":"by Rakshasa army"},{"d":"गुप्ताम्","m":"guarded"},{"d":"बहुभिः","m":"many"},{"d":"गुल्मैः","m":"posts"},{"d":"आवृताम्","m":"surrounded"},{"d":"पताकाध्वजमालिनीम्","m":"with rows of flags and posts and pennants तांनगरीम् that city"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"saw."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"रुद्धांतुनगरींदृष्टवारावणोराक्षसेश्वरः उवाचात्महितंकालेप्रहस्तंयुद्धकोविदम् ।","trans":"Ravana, the Lord of Rakshasas seeing the city besieged, spoke to Prahastha who was skilled in warfare for his welfare.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसेश्वरः","m":"Lord of Rakshasas"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"रुद्धाम्","m":"besieged"},{"d":"नगरीम्","m":"city"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"काले","m":"time"},{"d":"युद्धकोविदम्","m":"skilled in warfare"},{"d":"प्रहस्तम्","m":"Prahastha"},{"d":"आत्महितम्","m":"for his welfare"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"पुरस्योपनिविष्टस्यसहसापीडितस्यवा नान्यंयुद्धात्प्रपश्यामिमोक्षंयुद्धविशारद ।","trans":"\"I am not able to see anyone (other than you) knowledgeable in warfare to deliver the city oppressed suddenly and can liberate from war.\"","words":[{"d":"युद्धविशारद","m":"knowledgeable in war"},{"d":"उपनिविष्टस्य","m":"to deliver"},{"d":"सहसा","m":"suddenly"},{"d":"पीडितस्य","m":"oppressed"},{"d":"पुरस्य","m":"city's"},{"d":"युद्धात्","m":"from war"},{"d":"अन्यम्","m":"others"},{"d":"मोक्षम्","m":"can liberate"},{"d":"नप्रवश्यामि","m":"not able to know."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"अहंवाकुम्भकर्णोवात्वंवासेनापतिर्मम इन्द्रजिद्वानिकुम्भोवावहेयुर्भारमीदृशम् ।","trans":"\"Either myself or Kumbhakarna, or my CommanderinChief, or you, or Indrajith, or Nikumbha can undertake such a burden.\"","words":[{"d":"अहंवा","m":"myself"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णोवा","m":"or Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"सेनापतिः","m":"CommanderinChief"},{"d":"त्वंवा","m":"or you"},{"d":"इन्द्रजिद्वा","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"निकुम्भोवा","m":"or Nikumbha"},{"d":"ईदृशम्","m":"such"},{"d":"भारम्","m":"burden"},{"d":"वहेयुः","m":"undertake."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"सत्वंबलमतश्शीघ्रमादायपरिगृह्यच विजयायाभिनिर्याहियत्रसर्वेवनौकसः ।","trans":"\"Therefore, quickly get ready with the army and take charge for conquering the vanaras collected there.\"","words":[{"d":"सःत्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"ततः","m":"therefore"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"आदाय","m":"getting"},{"d":"परिगृह्यच","m":"taking charge"},{"d":"वनौकसः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"यत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"विजयाय","m":"for conquering"},{"