ncertain"},{"d":"आपत्","m":"if it comes"},{"d":"श्रेयः","m":"good"},{"d":"निस्सशयीकृता","m":"undesirable"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"तु","m":"you"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that"},{"d":"वा","m":"or"},{"d":"प्रतिलोमानुलोमंवा","m":"whether acceptable or not acceptable"},{"d":"हितम्","m":"good"},{"d":"मन्यसे","m":"I think."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"रावणेनैवमुक्तस्तुप्रहस्तोवाहिनीपतिः राक्षसेन्द्रमुवाचेदमसुरेन्द्रमिवोशना ।","trans":"Prahastha, the CommanderinChief having heard Ravana, replied to the king of Rakshasas just as the preceptor of Rakshasas spoke to Bali.","words":[{"d":"रावणेन","m":"by Ravana"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"spoken"},{"d":"वाहिनीपतिः","m":"CommanderinChief"},{"d":"उशना","m":"preceptor of Rakshasas"},{"d":"असुरेन्द्रमिव","m":"this way to the king of Rakshasas"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रम्","m":"Rakshasa Lord"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"राजन्मन्त्रितपूर्वंनःकुशलैस्सहमन्त्रिभिः विवादश्चापिनोवृत्तस्समवेक्ष्यपरस्परम् ।","trans":"\"O king! This was deliberated with capable ministers earlier, is it not It was reviewed with one another, and controversy arose.\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्","m":"O King!"},{"d":"कुशलैः","m":"capable"},{"d":"मन्त्रिभिःसह","m":"along with ministers"},{"d":"नः","m":"is it not"},{"d":"मन्त्रितपूर्वम्","m":"earlier"},{"d":"परस्परम्","m":"one another"},{"d":"समवेक्ष्य","m":"reviewed"},{"d":"नः","m":"is it not"},{"d":"विवादश्च","m":"controversy"},{"d":"वृत्तः","m":"arose."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"प्रदानेनतुसीतायाःश्रेयोव्यवसितंमया अप्रदानेपुनर्युद्धंदृष्टमेत्तथैवनः ।","trans":"\"If Sita is given away it is beneficial and if not given war is foreseen is known to us.\"","words":[{"d":"सीतायाः","m":"Sita"},{"d":"प्रदानेन","m":"by giving"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"श्रेयः","m":"beneficial"},{"d":"व्यवसितम्","m":"if not given"},{"d":"अप्रदानेपुनः","m":"not given"},{"d":"नः","m":"if not"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"war"},{"d":"दृष्टमेव","m":"foreseen."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"सोऽहंदानैश्चमानैश्चसततंपूजितस्त्वया सान्